channel.title: Need help with making a weblclient, with a jarred client! (free webclient)!
channel.description: Alright so I plan on just using a weebly.com. Here's my current site, it's plain, but that's because I'm waiting until I figure out how to get a webclient running on it. Alright so, I'm using the source named Vistex, so credits to him, but I did change stuff around so it's not the same thing as his server. If you're needing to know whether it's a 317 or 508 and what not, I want you to go to http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,541502.msg3966744.html#msg3966744 because I honestly can't figure out if it's 508 or not, I know it has 508 maps though. I do have the JARMaker and stuff, and I was following a tutorial on it, but he explained to find stuff in certain .java files and I couldn't find it, idk if it's because I may be on a different kind of server or what. But I just need someone to go through it with me. You can skype if you want, but I don't have a working mic. iamjmperry Or maybe send me to a link that you know would work. thanks
